{"tid":2007547,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普：可能是有人無能，導致病毒從武漢的研究所流出","createTime":"2020-05-08T11:25:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T15:32:22.000Z","uid":75656,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8d2e710803272c8960da7e6ef8e83053e3ae84ad","tid":2007547,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T11:25:24.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國總統特朗普再次批評中國未有在源頭阻截新冠病毒，又指可能是有人無能，導致病毒從武漢的研究所流出。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，眾議院共和黨領袖麥卡錫宣布，將會成立小組調查中國對美國的威脅，包括北京當局在新冠疫情所扮演的角色。他批評中國隱瞞疫情，阻止國際專家進行調查，又透過捐贈物資對其他國家施加影響力。<br />\n<br />\n小組將在十月，即美國大選前夕發表有關報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=390275\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D390275&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQFu%2BYei5PLor89YqF%2FSdhCs%3D&h=406818e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D390275&h=969beae6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=390275</a>"},{"pid":"1a91cb79812cdfa9e603fb57cf46abd7042d8fa4","tid":2007547,"uid":73111,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T11:49:33.000Z","msg":"又唔敢打仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b756ff9a96d1b81a69ef341c638aa98af2bd730","tid":2007547,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T15:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}